spec_data.Name: perl-Module-Runtime-Conflicts
spec_data.Description:
This module provides conflicts checking for Module::Runtime, which had a
recent release that broke some versions of Moose. It is called from
Moose::Conflicts and moose-outdated.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 01:36:45 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Provide information on conflicts for Module::Runtime
